						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying out side the village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Jagadēkamalla [Jayasiṁha II] 11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>In this very badly damaged inscription only Śrīmat-Jagadēkamalla can be made out. The purport of this 11th century A.D. character record is not clear. This Jagadēkamalla is the same as Chālukya Jayasiṁha II.</p>						

						</summary>
